## VMWare Install

Start by navigating to the [Broadcom Website](https://www.broadcom.com/) and creating an account.

Then navigate to the [VMware Workstation Pro](https://support.broadcom.com/group/ecx/productdownloads?subfamily=VMware+Workstation+Pro) download section and download the latest version for Windows in this example.

See the **[Ubuntu Install](https://github.com/Daboulch/VMware-Ubuntu-Tutorial/blob/main/Ubuntu%20Install)** page next!
